The paper discusses a methodology for classification of groups of examples, which is a common problem in image and video classification. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Among these, machine learning and computer vision are the most likely sub-categories as they are directly related to the problem discussed in the paper.
